{"lemma":"賱賽噩丕賲賹","slug":"賱賽噩丕賲賹","root":"賱.噩.賲","root_slug":"賱-噩-賲","root_link":"/words/roots/賱-噩-賲","pos":"N","pos_camel":"noun","paradigm":[],"frequency_in_corpus":0,"cross_references":{"qac":{"found":false},"wiktextract":{"found":true,"entry_count":1,"pos_tags":["noun"],"has_etymology":true,"sense_count":2},"lanes":{"found":true,"entry_ids":["n43237"],"search_url":"https://lanelexicon.com/?s=%D9%84%D9%90%D8%AC%D8%A7%D9%85%D9%8C"}},"translations":null,"definition":{"source":"wiktextract","senses":[{"pos":"noun","gloss":"a bridle bit","tags":["archaic","countable"]},{"pos":"noun","gloss":"a horse headcollar or headstall along with the reins; a bridle","tags":["countable"]}]},"etymology":{"source":"wiktextract","text":"From Classical Persian 賱诏丕賲 (lig膩m) or from an identical rare Aramaic term, see there."},"ipa":["/li.d汀蕭a藧m/"],"lanes_definition":{"source":"lanes","entries":[{"entry_id":"n43237","headword_ar":"賱賽噩賻丕賲賹","root":"ljm","body":[{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"A bit;"},{"kind":"text","text":"i. e.,"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"the iron appurtenances of a bridle"},{"kind":"text","text":"]. To the"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"ljAm","text_ar":"賱噩丕賲"},{"kind":"text","text":"belong pieces of iron which are fastened one to another; as the"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"EiDaAdataAni","text_ar":"毓賽囟賻丕丿賻鬲賻丕賳賽"},{"kind":"text","text":", and the"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"misoHal","text_ar":"賲賽爻賿丨賻賱"},{"kind":"text","text":", and the"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"faA^os","text_ar":"賮賻丕賿爻"},{"kind":"text","text":"and its extremities of iron. (Az, in TA, voce"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"qayoqabN","text_ar":"賯賻賷賿賯賻亘賹"},{"kind":"text","text":".) The above explanation is incomplete: it means the"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"bridle,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"headstall and reins, with the bit and other appurtenances;"},{"kind":"text","text":"like its Persian original,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"likaAmo","text_ar":"賱賽賰賻丕賲賿"},{"kind":"text","text":": see"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"qar~aTa","text_ar":"賯賻乇賻賾胤賻"},{"kind":"text","text":". It signifies The"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"piece of iron in the mouth of the horse:"},{"kind":"text","text":"thus, by extension, applied to"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"this with its thongs,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"straps, and apparatus:"},{"kind":"text","text":"it comprises the"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"$akiymap","text_ar":"卮賻賰賽賷賲賻丞"},{"kind":"text","text":", which is the transverse piece of iron in the mouth; and the"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"faA^os","text_ar":"賮賻丕賿爻"},{"kind":"text","text":", which is the piece of iron standing up in the mouth; and the"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"misoHal","text_ar":"賲賽爻賿丨賻賱"},{"kind":"text","text":", which is the iron beneath the"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Hanak","text_ar":"丨賻賳賻賰"},{"kind":"text","text":"; and the"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"xuT~aAfaAni","text_ar":"禺購胤賻賾丕賮賻丕賳賽"},{"kind":"text","text":", which are two bent pieces of iron in the"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"misoHal","text_ar":"賲賽爻賿丨賻賱"},{"kind":"text","text":"and the"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"$kymp","text_ar":"卮賰賷賲丞"},{"kind":"text","text":", on the right and left; and the"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"faraA$ataAni","text_ar":"賮賻乇賻丕卮賻鬲賻丕賳賽"},{"kind":"text","text":", which are two pieces of iron wherewith are fastened the extremities of the"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Ei*aAraAni","text_ar":"毓賽匕賻丕乇賻丕賳賽"},{"kind":"text","text":"; and the"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Hakamap","text_ar":"丨賻賰賻賲賻丞"},{"kind":"text","text":", which is the ring surrounding the"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"marosain","text_ar":"賲賻乇賿爻賻賽賳"},{"kind":"text","text":"and the"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Hanak","text_ar":"丨賻賳賻賰"},{"kind":"text","text":", of silver or iron or thong. (IDrd, in his Book on the Saddle and Bridle.)       -A2-  See"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"lujomahN","text_ar":"賱購噩賿賲賻賴賹"},{"kind":"text","text":"."}],"source_refs":[]}]},"classical_definitions":null}